Package: GOTeDNA
Type: Package
Title: Guidance on optimal eDNA sampling periods to develop, optimize, and interpret monitoring programs
Date: 2024-06-20
Version: 0.5.0.9005
Authors@R: c(person("Anaïs", "Lacoursière-Roussel et al.", email = "Anais.Lacoursiere@dfo-mpo.gc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Anais Lacoursiere-Roussel <anais.lacoursiere@dfo-mpo.gc.ca>
Description: The purpose of this package is to compile eDNA qPCR and    
    metabarcoding metadata and data, visualize species detection probabilities, and delineate species detection windows.
